ci-agent-one-click-apps
=======================

This repository contains one-click application templates for the ci-agent
deployment tool, in ci-agent's TOML catalog format.

The app templates under apps/ are derived from the CapRover One-Click Apps
project (https://github.com/caprover/one-click-apps), which is licensed under
the Apache License, Version 2.0. They were mechanically converted from
CapRover's captain-definition v4 YAML format into ci-agent's catalog TOML
format. The original copyright remains with the CapRover project and its
contributors. A copy of the Apache License 2.0 is included in LICENSE.

Conversion notes (see README.md for details): CapRover routes traffic through
its own reverse proxy using internal `srv-captain--` DNS names and a
`containerHttpPort`, whereas ci-agent publishes a host port on plain docker
compose. The conversion strips the `srv-captain--` prefix, publishes the web
port (or a known database/cache port) as `{{HTTP_PORT}}`, maps `$$cap_*`
variables to `{{...}}` placeholders, and escapes shell `$` so docker compose
does not interpolate it. Templates are best-effort and should be reviewed and
tested before production use.
